# Use Cases
 
Our system is build onto wifi networks which exist in physical spaces.  When we put media content on the network it attracts not merely "eyeballs" but physical people who must enter the space to participate in the network.  This allows digital media to be used to create physical shared spaces and community.  

 - Apartment building bulletin board for sharing waste-to-use resources, mutual aid
 - Medical literature in waiting room
 - Shopping center media network](scrolls/shoppingcenter)
 - Photo ad board
 - Music distribution through physical venues
